00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.720
pour vous.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:06.360
Tu es fini.

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:07.560
Tu as disparu pendant dix ans,

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:08.639
sans une seule explication.

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:10.680
Et maintenant, tu es soudainement à la maison.

00:08:11.279 --> 00:08:13.160
Maman et papa vont probablement te mettre dehors.

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:18.360
Quoi qu'il arrive,

00:08:18.839 --> 00:08:20.000
Je prendrai mes responsabilités.

00:08:21.519 --> 00:08:23.720
Quelle journée !

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:27.360
Tu es de retour, Yan.

00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:29.279
Maman.

00:08:30.079 --> 00:08:31.399
Tiens, prenons un peu de thé.

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:32.799
Dongfang Chen.

00:08:33.559 --> 00:08:34.600
Dongfang Chen !

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:36.000
Ne cours pas !

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.440
Oui.

00:08:36.440 --> 00:08:37.519
Tu es de retour.

00:08:40.600 --> 00:08:42.399
Tu es de retour, Yan.

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.360
